desc: As a plant lover I've decided to set up cactus plants shop online in the UK & share a little happiness with you all. Buy pretty cacti, mini succulents, leafy houseplants & more!

layout.text: Take a look at the range of small cactus, succulents and leaf house plants that come in 7cm nursery pots or smallest. There's even some tiny cactus plants in 3.5cm pots. Cute! 😍
